Zunda's collection of RPM spec files for Momonga Linux

To get started:

Have a look at
http://developer.momonga-linux.org/wiki/?OmoiKondaraQuickStart
follow the steps below:

  # yum install build-momonga
  $ mkdir ~/local/Momonga
  $ cd Momonga
  $ svn co http://svn.momonga-linux.org/svn/pkgs/trunk/tools
  $ cd Momonga
  $ git clone git://github.com/zunda/zunda-momonga-pkgs.git (or your folk)

You might want to replace zunda-momonga-pkgs/rpmrc with the one
from http://svn.momonga-linux.org/svn/pkgs/trunk/pkgs/rpmrc

  $ cd zunda-momonga-pkgs
  $ cp ../tools/example.OmoiKondara .OmoiKondara

Edit .OmoiKondara:
  TOPDIR ~/local/Momonga/PKGS
  PKGDIR ~/local/Momonga/zunda-momonga-pkgs

